{"tid":1268380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【圖輯】風雨無阻！年輕人參加撐警集會，為警隊加油!","createTime":"2019-06-30T09:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T09:51:49.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9d5c29d919bd773ab326940491eb270d938488","tid":1268380,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213158_875462.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213158_875462.jpg&h=536ec17b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213163_711770.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213163_711770.jpg&h=62af781d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【橙訊】由立法會議員何君堯和香港政研會主辦的「撐警隊，護法治，保安寧」集會，下午在金鐘添馬公園舉行。有到場集會的人士批評，部分反修訂《逃犯條例》的示威者行為有如暴民，感嘆警察在今次事件中受盡侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n集會於下午3時開始，參加者站滿公園草坪，添馬公園旁的中信大廈天橋出現人潮。集會人士大都響應呼籲穿上白衣或藍衣。有在場人士揮舞國旗，另有手持「阿Sir、Madam我撐你」、「支持警方嚴正執法」等標語，支持警方執法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213159_066342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213159_066342.jpg&h=7efbd06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213161_934902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213161_934902.jpg&h=952eade6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2da37721b9fb4dfc63d9392194e32ee5cddd1f75","tid":1268380,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"出席嘉賓包括基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠、全國政協常委譚錦球、全國政協委員兼警務處前處長鄧竟成、保公義撐修例大聯盟召集人兼全國政協委員黃英豪、工聯會會長兼港區全國人大代表吳秋北、港區全國人大代表王庭聰、民建聯監委會主席盧文端、藝人梁家輝、譚詠麟、鍾鎮濤等等。<br />\n<br />\n有到場集會的市民認為，在今次修例風波上，有人顛倒黑白，又不滿在反修例的示威中，有示威者堵塞道路。另有集會者批評部分示威者的抗爭手法太過分，特別是6.12金鐘警民衝突，在電視的新聞畫面上見到示威者向警方步步進逼；又不滿有人特地將當日的衝突，說成無示威者掟磚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213166_605523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213166_605523.jpg&h=672fb26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213168_471657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213168_471657.jpg&h=255d5d6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e4eaa219e3155427cab44fc8511912482453a5b","tid":1268380,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213162_206487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213162_206487.jpg&h=4aae34c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/31/10213165_342500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F31%2F10213165_342500.jpg&h=e1396a9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f79318c705e45d2c55de11d07a9d0c20f8cfef61","tid":1268380,"uid":157362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b1d22467c92a1ad4e5782cf7715834d30b0d1ff","tid":1268380,"uid":33848,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"年輕人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8534b2dc712359a34c489a47e60ddc8c1a59a9","tid":1268380,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"$1800"},{"pid":"a9df5b353ec22d847a0578f0ba30051ae5bf2590","tid":1268380,"uid":69999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我地一定係bb"},{"pid":"03f1c70d6711fd7e6ffd4477ef1dfedfb60e1db1","tid":1268380,"u